@startuml 02-maven-multimodule
title HexaStock — Maven Multi-Module Layout

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #1f4e79
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #1f4e79
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor #e7eef7

[domain]                                     as domain
[application]                                as app
[adapters-inbound-rest]                      as rest
[adapters-inbound-telegram]                  as tg
[adapters-outbound-persistence-jpa]          as jpa
[adapters-outbound-persistence-mongodb]      as mongo
[adapters-outbound-market]                   as market
[adapters-outbound-notification]             as notif
[bootstrap\n(Spring Boot main)]              as boot

app    --> domain
rest   --> app
tg     --> app
jpa    --> app
mongo  --> app
market --> app
notif  --> app
boot   --> rest
boot   --> tg
boot   --> jpa
boot   --> mongo
boot   --> market
boot   --> notif

note right of domain
  Pure Java. No Spring, no Jakarta,
  no JPA, no Jackson. Only the
  business model and exceptions.
end note

note right of app
  Use cases + ports (in/out).
  No Spring annotations
  (ADR-007). Only @Transactional
  from jakarta is allowed.
end note

note bottom of boot
  The ONLY Spring Boot module.
  Holds @Configuration, the main
  class, and the Spring Modulith
  @ApplicationModule declarations.
end note

@enduml
